author: Ryan Prior, CNN
title: Here's why you shouldn't try to conceive in quarantine
description: As much of the world settles into a new routine of social distancing, couples are likely to have a lot more free time to snuggle at home together. But there could be a number of risks in trying to get pregnant right now.
